***PLEASE READ ALL BEFORE PLAYING***

This is V2 of my map Before , it got rated poor because of the lighting , so i fixed that. And i thought..
Thats too little of a change to upload it to FPSBanana.. 
So i added a basement , and guns down there. and added lots of other random stuff.

The basement is a little darker , because its a basement..

I added two walk ways on the side , opposed to one in the middle.

Well , I really hope you enjoy this version. Alot better in my opinion..

Note: Its brighter in-game!
